videos.headline: Miami defense force fumble, return for TD
videos.description: After the Hurricanes' defense forces a fumble, Miami LB Shaquille Quarterman picks up the loose ball and returns it for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami defense returns failed pitch for touchdown
videos.description: Georgia Tech QB Justin Thomas fumbles the ball after failing to make a clean pitch. Miami defensive lineman Joe Jackson picks up the loose ball returning it 18 yards for the Hurricanes' second defensive touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: J. Thomas pass,to D. Mills for 9 yds for a TD
videos.description: Justin Thomas pass complete to Dedrick Mills for 9 yds for a TD

videos.headline: D. Mills scores for his third total touchdown of the game
videos.description: Dedrick Mills run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: Kaaya slings it to Coley for 31-yard TD extending Canes' lead
videos.description: Miami QB Brad Kaaya completes a pass over the middle to Stacy Coley who takes it into the end zone for a 31-yard touchdown reception which extends the Hurricanes' lead over Georgia Tech by two touchdowns.

videos.headline: Miami defense comes up big again and forces another turnover to seal the game
videos.description: Justin Thomas pass intercepted Michael Pinckney return for 2 yds to the MiaFl 21
